								"name": "Paragraph",
								"type": "textarea",
								"html": "<p>\n\tNorth Carolina ranks&nbsp;among the top 10 states for human trafficking. In 2023, the National Human Trafficking Hotline identified nearly 400 victims of trafficking in North Carolina. That figure is likely much higher because trafficking is a hidden crime. The Salvation Army is committed to increasing community awareness, education and assistance for victims.\n</p>",
